Morris Edward WALLACE v. C. H. LOONEY, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Leavenworth, Kansas. No. 5795. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. March 11, 1958. William C. Farmer, U. S. Atty., and E. Edward Johnson, Asst. U. S. Atty., Topeka, Kan., for appellee.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and HUXMAN and MURRAH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed without written opinion.
